column2: SELECT s.bestObjID, z.objid, s.specObjID, z.specobjid,   z.ra, z.dec, s.z, z.nvote,  g.dered_u, g.dered_g, g.dered_r, g.dered_i, g.dered_z,  z.p_el, z.p_cw, z.p_acw, z.p_edge, z.p_dk, z.p_mg, z.p_cs,   z.p_el_debiased, z.p_cs_debiased, z.spiral, z.elliptical, z.uncertain FROM zooSpec as z JOIN specObj AS s ON s.bestObjID = z.objid JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID = z.objID WHERE s.class = &&&  AND z.p_mg BETWEEN # and #  AND (s.legacy_target1 & (# | # | #)) > #  AND s.z BETWEEN # and # ORDER BY z.ra
